channel.title: 1 easy compile error
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape,I've never had this compile error before: [code]client.java:3536: illegal start of expression public void fromBank(int itemID, int fromSlot, int amount) { ^ 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Please Help.

Hello Moparscape,I’ve never had this compile error before:

client.java:3536: illegal start of expression public void fromBank(int itemID, int fromSlot, int amount) { ^ 1 error Press any key to continue . . .
